com.upsight.android.analytics.internal.dispatcher

Class Dispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.upsight.android.analytics.internal.dispatcher.Dispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnResponseListener, RoutingListener

    public class Dispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements RoutingListener
    The component responsible for getting DataStoreRecords delivered to the server endpoints and notifying the system of server responses.
